            "text": " an inquiry. Frank’s column argues that if the lab-leak theory is proven true — or even partly true — it will be a huge blow against the entire notion of expertise, after a year in which political and media elites insisted that the hypothesis wasn’t even worthy of legitimate discussion.",
            "type": "text",
