          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "To be sure, bad-faith right-wing actors have been trying to manipulate the story about the COVID-19 pandemic to gin up hostility against China — and if the Wuhan lab-leak theory has any merit, they will use that to try to fuel their dangerous political agenda. But here’s the key question: Should politically inconvenient facts and scientific inquiry be avoided just because bad-faith voices will inevitably try to distort them?",
